Module kivakit.resource
Package com.telenav.kivakit.resource.spi

Interface ResourceResolver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    File.Resolver, PackageResource.Resolver
    public interface ResourceResolver
    Service provider interface that resolves resource identifiers to resources. If the resolver returns true from accepts(ResourceIdentifier), then the resource identifier can be resolved to a Resource by resolve(ResourceIdentifier). Resource resolution permits a very broad abstraction to be used when denoting resources with strings. In particular, it is possible to accept an arbitrary string, like a command line switch, and convert this value into a Resource that can subsequently be read.
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
